qMeasure.qDef:
rangemin(1, 
    pick(match(v_ViewUptake, 'FIRST', 'SECOND', 'ADD'),
      sum({<[Member State]=>} [Uptake1st_$(v_ViewTargetGroup)]),
      sum({<[Member State]=>} [Uptake2nd_$(v_ViewTargetGroup)]),
      sum({<[Member State]=>} [UptakeAdd_$(v_ViewTargetGroup)])
    )
)
qMeasure.qLabelExpression:
= pick(match(v_ViewUptake, 'FIRST', 'SECOND', 'ADD'), 'Uptake at least one dose (%)', 'Uptake full vaccination (%)', 'Uptake of additional doses (%)') 
& ' - ' & 
pick(match(v_ViewTargetGroup, '80', '70', '60', '50', 'HCW', 'LTCF'), 
'80 years old and above',
'70 years old and above',
'60 years old and above',
'50 years old and above',
'Healthcare Workers',
'LTCF residents'
)

qMetaDef.title: TG - Uptake Current
qMetaDef.description: Uptake at least one dose or full vaccination for select target group
